{"tid":19522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（穆斯林系列3）巴基斯坦青年被四青年輪姦","createTime":"2016-12-02T23:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T00:33:45.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9150c94d94ecf2ddfe462944a58e9c460f9e5686","tid":19522,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T23:29:49.000Z","msg":"希臘萊斯沃斯島（Lesbos）的難民營人滿為患，&hellip;&hellip;島上其中一個難民營周日發生輪姦事件，一名16歲的巴基斯坦青年被4名未成年同胞性侵，涉案人士已被拘捕。&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n據悉，涉嫌輪姦的4名難民，年齡為16至17歲，與受害人同樣來自巴基斯坦。<br />\n<br />\n希臘警方已安排案中疑犯，於周三出庭應訊。"},{"pid":"722a5dcb554769249650f1a2e0467098a4d74d08","tid":19522,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T23:35:10.000Z","msg":"雞姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁既宗教 唔接受到世界文化 又唔係同世界價值觀一致 成日迫害其他宗教既人 呢個宗教有乜用"},{"pid":"4560f901c2128bd8b31c6e1a1c57e5787c36e862","tid":19522,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T23:37:31.000Z","msg":"大家都係巴基躝癱<br />\n包容啦"},{"pid":"79f6ea1a47720e46a1ab47ced804030d8a233236","tid":19522,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T00:33:45.000Z","msg":"根本輪姦就係佢地文化不可分割既一部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}